The '''Great Downrush''' was the largest river on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]]. It was fed by several tributaries, including the [[Grandmother's Tears]] and a stream originating at the [[Trundur Wall]]. The river was a kilometer wide when it passed [[Pelek Baw/Legends|Pelek Baw]], and at the south of the city it went into the [[Downrush Falls]].

